# Pin Generator
# Called by multi-domain-clean. In multi-domain-clean/.env set:
#   PIN_API_URL=http://<this-host>:5000
# Docker Compose service names with underscores (e.g. pin_generator) are rewritten
# internally so Werkzeug 3.2+ host checks do not reject them; or use a hostname with
# hyphens only (e.g. network alias pin-generator) in PIN_API_URL.

# Run API: python generator.py --serve --port 5000
# Optional: AI keys, R2_* for upload (see generator.py)
